gomodel:SYNGO_16  a       owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Automated change 2024-03-14: GO:0099055 replaced by GO:0045211" , "Rationale: Purkinje cell dendritic spines (sp) receiving asymmetrical synapses from parallel fiber terminals (PFT) are Kv3.3 immunopositive.\n\n5/12/2016 Pim\n- The integral component of the annotation was derived from the TM-domains of KCNC3.\n- Literal Fig.2: \"Purkinje cell dendritic spines ( sp ) receiving asymmetrical synapses from parallel fiber terminals ( PFT ) are Kv3.3 immunopositive ( arrows in a - e ). Silver particles are positioned perisynaptically but also in **extrasynaptic positions ( arrows in a - e ) along the spine membranes**.\". Experimental description: Results Fig 2: \"Fig. 1 Subcellular compartmentalization of Kv3.1b in the **rat** cerebellar molecular layer. Pre-embedding immunogold method for electron microscopy using parasagittal cerebellar sections.....\"" ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
        dc:contributor    "https://orcid.org/0000-0001-9425-2935" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2514-0216" ;
        dc:date           "2024-03-14" ;
        dc:title          "SYNGO_CC_16" ;
        pav:providedBy    "https://syngo.vu.nl" ;
        biolink:in_taxon  "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/NCBITaxon_10116" .

